trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Data.XmlNamespaceMapping"></xref> objects.

The <xref:System.Windows.Data.XmlNamespaceMapping> class provides a mapping between the namespace specified in your [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)] binding source and a prefix you specify that you can use in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)].
